genresAdvancedInfo.name: german dark minimal techno
genresAdvancedInfo.description: German dark minimal techno is a subgenre of techno that is characterized by its dark and atmospheric soundscapes. It often features sparse, repetitive beats and haunting melodies, and is popular among fans of underground electronic music.
